partnerDetails.about: Union Electrical Wholesalers was established in 1974 to service an industrial, mine and electrical contractor client base with all their electrical requirements. The company has grown steadily in its 43 years of existence and has become a well known name in the electrical supply and wholesale business. It has become a successful operation that has been run efficiently by its management.
